<br>
If you summon it while already having 1 or more of the items on you, you get the usual duplicate message, but then you also get a set of 'Duplicate Item Deleted' messages. The summoned bag will then not have any of the items you were already wearing. <br>
<br>
This is where the bug comes in. On several occasions, the items I was wearing when I summoned the bag have immediately ceased to function. I've tried swapping them around (i.e. moving to other wrist/finger/ear), and that didn't seem to help. Some 10-15 minutes later I opened up my inventory, and lo and behold, the items were now GONE.<br>
<br>
Moral of the story, toss all your items before summoning a bag, even if you're doing it to get an item you don't currently have on you. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=3284">Sarelorn Stonecaller</a><BR>
Arch Convoker<BR>
<a href="http://www.chinhole.net/eq">Sol Invictus</a><BR>
